title: W.I.T.C.H.: The Graphic Novel, Part IX. 100% W.I.T.C.H., Vol. 3
description: The Magic in the Mundane Having defeated countless enemies, the girls are always on high alert...but when an attack finally does come, it’s from a surprising enemy—the Earth itself! From grappling with the elements to struggling with relationships, there’s never a quiet day for W.I.T.C.H.!
author: Walt Disney Company
